---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Logos AI"
	description="Why the Logos AI blog exists."
	pubDate={new Date('March 26 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Logos AI is being built as a free Bible study app with optional upgrades, not as a locked-down AI demo that asks
		for payment before value is clear.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is where product reasoning, release notes, packaging decisions, and longer-form thinking live while the
		main site stays focused on conversion, downloads, and clear positioning.
	</p>

	<p>
		The standard is practical usefulness: make reading and study easier, respect privacy and offline needs, and keep
		paying users focused on convenience gains rather than forced access.
	</p>
</Layout>
